title: Deana Carter - Did I Shave My Legs for This [1995] Original UK R
description:
Did I Shave My Legs for This [1995] Original UK Version
EAC Lame 320kbps Joint Stereo

An alternate album was released in the UK in 1995. The UK version had a completely different set of tracks that never made it onto her North America version of the album. Three tracks were used on the North America release, and three other tracks were later used on The Deana Carter Collection. "Angel Without a Prayer" was released as a promotional single in 1995, along with a music video.

I borrowed the CD of this album from a public library back in the 90s when it first came out and copied it to Chrome Audio Cassette and Normal Audio Cassette. The Chrome copy was kept as back up and never played. This has been encoded from THAT back up tape. The album is extremely rare and I could not even find a decent picture of the cover on the net.
